SYSTEM: Sparqlex.pdf: Página 10
Queries about the instances
• Give me all the places and their population, 
ordering the results by the name of the place 
ascending
PREFIX pr: <http://GP-onto.fi.upm.es/Practica2#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?x ?y  WHERE { $place pr:NumeroHabitantes ?y;
rdfs:label ?x.}
ORDER BY ASC(?x)
speaker: SYSTEM
